erate. Therefore, social\nassistance dependency may be a multilevel process. Future research is to\nexplore how the mediating effects of disadvantaged neighborhoods vary in\ndifferent contexts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 21:36:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2022 16:39:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2022 17:59:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-18"}
