ep the same writing structure for all three parts so that all common ideas\nand developments appears exactly the same. We believe this choice to be\ncoherent to facilitate the reader's understanding. Finally, these are\npreliminary versions of the final papers: for each parts the theory is fully\ndescribed, but, although they have been implemented, the examples and\nalgorithms sections are not always complete. This will be mentioned in the\nintroductions of the concerned sections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2022 15:01:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 18:53:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-28"}
