lly, we introduce future research opportunities. In a\nnutshell, this paper investigates the fundamentals of SemCom, its applications\nin 6G networks, and the existing challenges and open issues for further\ndirection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2022 12:08:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 13 Nov 2022 14:10:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-15"}
